{"type":null,"faqId":49877,"title":"华为智能手表_真皮表带怎么保养？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body56640484\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__ul46013667\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li40002310\">真皮表带应置于通风、透气、干燥的地方。如表带弄脏、弄湿，应及时用干净软棉布抹净皮带上的水份或污物，放置于通风阴凉处干燥后，再用皮具光亮保护剂涂刷一层。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li24476477\">请勿将真皮表带放在烈日下暴晒，或使用微波炉、吹风机等外部加热设备对潮湿的真皮表带进行干燥处理，否则皮表面会出现收缩或膨胀现象。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li18961705\">避免真皮表带与粗糙或尖锐物接触及摩擦，以免造成损坏。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li36437619\">请勿超负荷挤压、长期弯曲皮表带，以免变形。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li59503116\">请勿将真皮表带靠近易燃物品及各种酸、碱性物质。皮料上的毛孔或皮纹属自然形成不属保养范围。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li65765997\">真皮表带不能卷得过紧，容易起皱。请勿从反面倒折表带，这样会造成正面无法恢复平滑，损坏表带。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329065__li55023063\">请勿私自打孔，打孔后如果没有专业的涂油保护会导致真皮表带破裂。</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":494,"faqType":"维护与保养","useful":5,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329065","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Maintenance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615862000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":128,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"表带，皮带，养护，保养","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}